name: Writercloudtexts
body:
### Welcome to Writer Cloud Texts
Please download the bin package if you want to use the application as and end-user.
Just download everything [there](https://github.com/IBMKuehlschrank/WriterCloudTexts/tree/master/bin/Debug)and run the .exe file.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
